casebody.data:
Decided 8 January, 1900. ZIMMERMAN v. BARLOW. From Clackamas : Thos. A. McBride, Judge.

Action on accountin Justice’s Court,Clackamas County. Judgment for plaintiff. Defendant appealed to circuit court. Verdict for the defendant by direction of court. From this judgment, plaintiff takes this appeal. Dismissed upon stipulation of parties. No opinion.

Dismissed.
